headline: A $20 Billion Fund Puts Its Religious Stamp on Corporate America
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Jim Lake, a devout Christian in Washington state, said his religious beliefs have always made him opposed to practices such as abortion, transgender transitions or embryonic stem cell research.
